title: You're Looking Snazzy Today
description: 20 Questions - MN edition, War of the Roses, Callie from Group Therapy on Tuesday calls in to update us on her guy situation, Dave got sad about getting rid of something sentimental, a listener that was debating opening a letter he recently got from someone of his past tells us what he decided to do, Dave & Susan got caught doing something hilarious at a restaurant over the weekend, and more!
